<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cruel-adj">cruel <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kruːəl/    美 /'kruːəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>残忍的；残酷的；无情的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 kind </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some people choose not to eat meat because they believe that it is <strong>cruel to</strong> eat animals.
有些人不吃肉，因为他们觉得吃动物太残忍。</p><footer>2012 广东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was cruel of Jim to ignore her.
吉姆存心不理会她，真是无情。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
